Servlet Config
inside Web.xml-->inside Servlet tag create init-param
and provide the param-name===>any name we can provide
param-value=====>database url
one object for every servlet is created by webcontainer
	<servlet>
		<servlet-name>B</servlet-name>
		<servlet-class>com.jsp.Servlet1</servlet-class>


		<init-param>
			<param-name>url</param-name>
			<param-value>jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/university</param-value>
		</init-param>
	</servlet>
